      "updated": 1773057915416,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Scenario 2:\n- Access private resources from a pipeline through a\nVNet/onprem data gw.\n- For the private DB you can use Azure DB.\n- You can use either VNet or onprem data gateways.\nVNDGs are easier to provision.\n- You can move data between AzDB and AzStorage\nor between AzDB and OneLake.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Scenario 2:\n- Access private resources from a pipeline through a VNet/onprem data gw.\n- For the private DB you can use Azure DB.\n- You can use either VNet or onprem data gateways. VNDGs are easier to provision.\n- You can move data between AzDB and AzStorage or between AzDB and OneLake.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
